[
    [
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Acquiring Images with GigE Vision Cameras "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                93,
                460,
                108
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "本主题包含以下部分："
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                112,
                317,
                126
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "list",
            "content": {
                "list_type": "text_list",
                "list_items": [
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": " Acquirinq Imaqes with a CCD Camera and Frame Grabber "
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": ". Acquiring Images with a CDC Camera and Frame Grabber "
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": " Acquiring Imaqes with a Line Scan Camera "
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "Acquirinq Imaqes with GiqE Vision Cameras "
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                157,
                130,
                606,
                212
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "本节提供有关在 VisionPro 和 Visual Studio 应用程序中使用 GigE 视觉摄像机的信息。GigE相机不使用帧抓取器，而是连接到一个千兆以太网网络适配器连接到您的计算机。有关配置QuickBuild应用程序以使用GigE Vision摄像机的信息，请参阅配置图像源。要使用 GigE Vision camera，必须在安装在计算机上的 Cognex 帧捕捉器、与之连接的Cognex 加密狗或通过 Cognex 软件许可证启用 VxSWAcquisition 安全位。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                223,
                855,
                313
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "注意:请务必阅读 VisionPro 工具包附带的 GigE Vision Cameras 用户指南，学习如何创建相机网络，如何将相机连接到网络，以及如何为相机分配IP地址。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                334,
                850,
                368
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "GigE Vision Acquisition Overview（GigE 视觉取像概述） "
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                390,
                623,
                406
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "要从GigE相机获取图像，您使用的技术与使用cognex提供的帧抓取器获取图像的技术完全相同。唯一的区别是，ICogFrameGrabber接口是一个物理的GigE相机，而不是一个帧抓取器。以下部分列出了获取图像的步骤。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                426,
                850,
                481
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Get a CogFrameGrabberGigEs Object "
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                502,
                487,
                517
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "第一步是获得一个 CogFrameGrabberGigEs 对象。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                538,
                574,
                554
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "这个对象是单个帧抓取对象的集合，每个对象都通过 ICogFrameGrabber 接口访问。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                556,
                830,
                571
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "每个 ICogFrameGrabber 表示与计算机系统相连的 GigE 相机。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                574,
                663,
                590
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "CogFrameGrabberGigEs cameras "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\cdot"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "new CogFrameGrabberGigEs(); "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                594,
                657,
                608
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "四、Enumerate the Connected Cameras（枚举连接的相机）"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                631,
                589,
                646
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "创建了CogFrameGrabberGigEs对象之后，就可以枚举它的内容，为每个连接的摄像机获取一个 ICogFrameGrabber 接口。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                668,
                848,
                702
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Count属性返回连接到您的系统的GigE相机的数量。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                705,
                591,
                721
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "你可以使用Item属性(或者c#中的索引器)来获得一个单独的相机。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                722,
                692,
                739
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "如果相机还没有连接好计算机，他们将不被包括在计数中，并且你将无法得到他们的参考。在启动应用程序之前，请确保您的相机已经完全通电、连接到网络并配置好。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                741,
                847,
                776
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "ICogFrameGrabber接口的Name属性将返回相机的制造商名称和型号。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                778,
                739,
                794
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "CogFrameGrabberGigEs cameras "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\cdot"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "new CogFrameGrabberGigEs(); "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                816,
                657,
                831
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "ICogFrameGrabber camera "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\cdot"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "cameras[0]; "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                834,
                480,
                848
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "System.Diagnostics.Debug.WriteLine(camera.Name); "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                853,
                561,
                868
            ]
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "五、 Select a Supported Video Format and Create a CogAcqFifo"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                147,
                93,
                635,
                109
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "一 旦 获 得 了 ICogFrameGrabber 接 口 ， 就 可 以 使 用 支 持 的 视 频 格 式 调 用 其CreateAcqFifo 函数来获得 ICogAcqFifo。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                130,
                847,
                164
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "个版本的 VisionPro 支持在 VisionPro 的摄像机支持主题中列出的 GigE Vision 视频格式。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                167,
                847,
                200
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "algorithm",
            "content": {
                "algorithm_caption": [],
                "algorithm_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "const stringVIDEO_FORMAT  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "="
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " \"Generic GigEVision (Bayer Color)\";   \nICogAcqFifofifo  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "="
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " camera.CreateAcqFifo(   \nVIDEO_FORMAT,   \nCogAcqFifoPixelFormatConstants.Format8Grey,   \n0, true); "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                215,
                204,
                707,
                293
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "通用的GigE vision视频格式不指定图像大小。为了确定获得的图像的实际大小，在创建了采集FIFO之后立即得到感兴趣的区域，如下图所示:"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                297,
                847,
                331
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "algorithm",
            "content": {
                "algorithm_caption": [],
                "algorithm_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "ICogAcqROI ROIParams;   \nint x, y, width, height   \nROIParams  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "="
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " myAcqFifo.OwnedROIParameters;   \nif (ROIParams != null)   \nOIParams.GetROIXyWidthHeight(x, y, width, height); "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                216,
                335,
                601,
                442
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "六、 Use the CogAcqFifo to Acquire Images "
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                464,
                494,
                480
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "一旦创建了 ICogAcqFifo，就可以使用标准方法获取图像。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                501,
                628,
                516
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "七、 GigE Vision Camera Feature Support "
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                146,
                539,
                480,
                554
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "许多常用的GigE vision相机功能都是通过VisionPro图像采集属性直接支持的。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                575,
                794,
                590
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "对于VisionPro不直接支持的特性，可以使用 ICogGigEAccess接口来获取和设置特性。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                593,
                847,
                627
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "阅 "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\%"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "VPRO_ROOT%\\Samples\\Programming\\Acquisition\\GigEVisionProperties 中 的示例代码，了解如何做到这一点。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                631,
                847,
                665
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "注意:如果在 VisionPro 脚本中使用特性设置和获取方法，则必须将调用封装在 try/catch块中。如果您不使用try/catch块，您的脚本可能会导致您的作业超时。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                686,
                848,
                721
            ]
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "table",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/a52c896eee6bbaf6c47f9015b292cc5f644c01639c7638b87ca98c1e2f087e39.jpg"
                },
                "table_caption": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Table 1. GenICam features supported by VisionPro "
                    }
                ],
                "table_footnote": [],
                "html": "<table><tr><td>GenICam Feature</td><td>VisionPro Property</td><td>Comments</td></tr><tr><td>AcquisitionMode</td><td></td><td>Controlled by the combination of TriggerModel</td></tr><tr><td>AcquisitionStart</td><td></td><td>TriggerEnabled and StartAcquire</td></tr><tr><td>AcquisitionStop</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>PixelFormat</td><td></td><td>Based on video format used</td></tr><tr><td>TriggerMode</td><td>ICogAcqTrigger</td><td>Based on current TriggerModel</td></tr><tr><td>ExposureTime</td><td>ICogAcqExposure</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>BlackLevel</td><td>ICogAcqBrightness</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Gain</td><td>ICogAcqContrast</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>OffsetX</td><td>ICogAcqROI</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>OffsetY</td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Width</td><td>ICogAcqROI</td><td></td></tr><tr><td>Height</td><td></td><td></td></tr></table>",
                "table_type": "simple_table",
                "table_nest_level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                184,
                107,
                878,
                268
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "要了解如何使用时间戳来检测 GigE视觉摄像机错过的图像或错过的触发器，请参阅使用GigE视觉摄像机的时间戳。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                278,
                848,
                313
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "八、 Debugging GigE Vision Applications "
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                335,
                473,
                351
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "GigE相机要求应用程序定期向相机发送一个网络数据包，称为心跳，以表明应用程序正在与相机通信。如果相机在超时时间结束前没有收到心跳脉冲，它将关闭与应用程序的连接。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                370,
                848,
                423
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "默认心跳超时时间为3秒。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                181,
                426,
                386,
                442
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "在调试GigE Vision应用程序时，您将希望增加心跳超时时间间隔，以便在您处于断点时相机不会脱机。您可以添加以下代码到您的程序:"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                463,
                848,
                499
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "ifdef DEBUG//defined for MS Visual Studio debug builds //Set timeout to 1 minute (unit is mSec) camera.gigECameraAcess.SetIntegerFeature(\"GevHeartbeatTimeout\",60\\*1000); #endif "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "java"
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                519,
                806,
                589
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "九、 Saving and Restoring Camera State（保存和重置相机状态）"
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                612,
                653,
                627
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "通过使用相机的UserSetSave命令，您可以将您更改的任何功能的状态保存到相机的内存中:"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                649,
                847,
                682
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "code",
            "content": {
                "code_caption": [],
                "code_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "camera.SetFeature(\"UserSetDefaultSelector\", \"UserSet1\");  \ncamera.SetFeature(\"UserSetSelector\", \"UserSet1\");  \ncamera.ExecuteCommand(\"UserSetSave\"); "
                    }
                ],
                "code_language": "javascript"
            },
            "bbox": [
                215,
                686,
                650,
                739
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "十、 Working with Bayer Images "
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                144,
                760,
                416,
                777
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "转换拜耳格式图像的 VisionPro例程要求图像的像素和行数为偶数，左上角的像素是拜耳模式的开始。VisionPro GigE视觉采集软件调整感兴趣区域(ROI)，以确保满足这些条件。图像的实际ROI可能比您要求的更窄或更短两个像素。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                179,
                797,
                848,
                851
            ]
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/1924d50bd135bdfdcfdbbcb119d9968b188c115295baf2dbf417b36f67852475.jpg"
